Allows you to change your field of view for both the world and each weapon type.

Vanilla jump has the FOV lower back to the set World FOV when in the air.
For multiplayer, all players need to set their world FOV to that of the host.

Notes for modders, this mod changes:
	InitialDuration of gd_skills_common.Basic.Melee
	Where gd_skills_common.Basic.DoubleTime is in the BasicSkills list